Comment:
The one good thing about this trailer for me is "Diesel Weasel" being back. If they really want to make one last chapter we could enjoy and take seriously, they should do a story about the humans returning to start occupying the land now that it's warmer. 

It would be a territorial drama about the gang trying to find a new home while staying ahead of the tribe, which would be led by the now grown up human Manny, Sid, and Diego helped get back to his father as a baby in the original. When the chips are down though, they'd have to hope that the kid can remember the animals who saved his life. Manny would be in a position where he must choose between possibly killing the boy he once protected like his own child or risk losing his family as he did before.

Now THAT'S how you deliver an Ice Age finale! But no, instead, we get more of this pandering silliness. Sigh...
